<li>Many of the tools needed to run a family are the same as that you need to run a business.</li>

<li>Making big decision up front will allow you to make smaller decisions faster. This book advocates taking serious time to think about the question of family meals.</li>

<li>This book is at its core a business book.</li>

<li>Suggest you actually sit down and work out what you want your life to look like. Once you know some basic principles many decisions can be "triaged". <a href="Protocols.html#ID-AFC02299-8850-4092-87F7-EFD1195F7359">Protocols</a></li>

